## Attribution

This project replicates and extends data from:

Shaikh, Anwar (2016). *Capitalism: Competition, Conflict, Crises*.
Oxford University Press. ISBN 978-0199390632.

Original data appendices available at: http://www.anwarshaikhecon.org/

All extension data is drawn from publicly available government statistical
agencies (FRED, BEA, BLS, World Bank, MeasuringWorth, OECD).
